  "body": "Anecdotal reports of Besu clients being dropped by Geth clients. \n\n### Description\nAs a Besu Dev, I want to understand Geth peering behavior so that Besu can maintain Geth peers. \n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n* Understand how Geth manages peer reputation, and reasons for disconnecting\n* Understand if there are improvements we can make in Besu to increase our peer reputation\n* Doc relevant parts of the code - \npivot block - and how do we select which peer to download info from\n\n",
